{"tid":1709947,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"科大宣佈戒嚴","createTime":"2019-11-12T04:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T06:28:43.000Z","uid":18265,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"2776c8e377d16fa091dc0799df1e10e2a3067726","tid":1709947,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:41:35.000Z","msg":"We would like to communicate more information about the new security measures on campus:<br />\n <br />\n1. Since the events of last week, the university has<span style=\"color: red;\"> doubled the number of campus security personnel to take us to over 100 security staff on duty day and night</span>. In addition, the responsibilities of some members of FMO senior management have been reassigned to ensure sufficient senior management attention and support for the enhanced security measures.  <br />\n<br />\n2. Additional security personnel will be stationed at all student residences and staff quarters. There will be at least one member of security<span style=\"color: red;\"> on duty 24/7 at each student hostel and staff residence tower</span>. Security at off campus sites such as the TKO student hostel, 1 University Road and the Junior Staff Quarters complex will be increased significantly and also operate 24/7.<br />\n<br />\n3. The access controls at North and South Gates will ensure that <span style=\"color: red;\">only students, staff, family members and helpers, alumni, authorised contractors and pre-registered visitors will be allowed to enter campus.</span> The university will help all campus residents to obtain the necessary identification if necessary. Pre-registered visitors must provide a valid invitation from the university to enter campus. Visitors that have not pre-registered will only be allowed onto campus if they have a valid reason for the visit, bring personal identification and register at the entrance gates. In the interest of efficiency all students and staff are urged to pre-register visitors. In the event that the new access controls are breached with malicious intent, the University will automatically request police support.<br />\n<br />\n4. In light of the recent tensions, the university has updated its internal protocol for requesting police support. The safety of all students and staff remains the top priority for the university.<br />\n <br />\nThe new access controls may result in delays in entering campus and we ask for understanding and cooperation at this difficult time. <br />\n <br />\nThe university urges all of its members to remain calm, adopt a safety-first approach and avoid confrontation at any level.<br />\n <br />\nOffice of the Vice-President for Administration and Business"},{"pid":"215d769bb5fd2230cf606062bcc214c295563f40","tid":1709947,"uid":35658,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:43:11.000Z","msg":"屎維佢到底will be outraged 左未?"},{"pid":"4dd4df8fe01749112b7c5ae80df77bd52c112647","tid":1709947,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:43:13.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"cf92e492ff9b90c34b228a721426390eb945cfb1","tid":1709947,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"215d769bb5fd2230cf606062bcc214c295563f40","tid":1709947,"uid":35658,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:43:11.000Z","msg":"屎維佢到底will be outraged 左未?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:43:32.000Z","msg":"捉緊私了支那仔嘅手足，等下啦"},{"pid":"a49573a910cf470cb6342a5ae42a1fee1e4c5e3f","tid":1709947,"uid":273228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"215d769bb5fd2230cf606062bcc214c295563f40","tid":1709947,"uid":35658,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:43:11.000Z","msg":"屎維佢到底will be outraged 左未?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:43:55.000Z","msg":"有呀<br />\n向一眾local lo <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1076d9343a